metadata.name: Proposal
metadata.description:
One of the most impotrtant decision in our lives! 
“Will you marry me?!”  
He took her near the beach to have fun together but suddenly a helicopter appeared in the sky, having a message: “will you marry me?!”  
At this breath taking moment she said “Yes, ofcourse” while her eyes were shining and yeah we have a party near the beach now! join us :)
